quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,"Toto efwe khwakhwishilia Ikurani indutu, indutu"
  76,24,"Kho linda okhula shingala Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi alabusia, ne alaulila yesiyesi mubo owetsimbi nohomba omukhayi tawe"
  76,25,Ne itsulila elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nibushia nende nibwila
  76,26,"Ne mushilo omwinamile ye, ne umwitsomie uluwono olurambi"
  76,27,"Toto Abandu bano bachama obulamu bwokhushialo, nebalekhanga inyuma wabu inyanga isiro"
  76,28,"Efwe khabaloonga, ne nikhubaramwo amani, nenikhwenya khunyala okhukalukhasia abandi bali shingabo"
  76,29,"Toto bwene kano ni ametsulisio, ne owenya atile injila itsia awa Nyasaye wuwe"
  76,30,"Neshimwakhenya tawe okhula Nyasaye achame, toto bwene Nyasaye niye omumanyi muno, owamachesi po"
  76,31,"Yenjisinjia owayenya mutsimbabasi tsitsie, ne abamayanu yabarecheshela eshinyasio eshilulu"